(5301, 'Galvus met 50/500mg 30 f.c.tabs', 'جالفس ميت 50/500مجم 30 قرص', '194', '258', 'Metformin hydrochloride+vildagliptin', 'Novartis', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Anti-diabetic.combined secretagogues+sensitizers', '500mg', '**Metformin immediate-release formulations**
